---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Shipping Policy | The Candle Sleeves"
  description="Shipping Policy for The Candle Sleeves — learn about production lead times, shipping carriers, delivery timelines, and tracking for custom candle sleeve orders."
  canonical="https://thecandlesleeves.com/shipping-policy"
  noindex={true}
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Shipping Policy</h1>
      <p>Last updated: May 2025</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <p>This Shipping Policy outlines how The Candle Sleeves handles production, packaging, and delivery of your custom candle sleeve orders across the United States.</p>

      <h2>1. Production Lead Times</h2>
      <p>Because every order is custom-manufactured to your specifications, production begins only after:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your digital artwork proof has been reviewed and approved in writing</li>
        <li>The required deposit or full payment has been received</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Standard production lead times are <strong>7 to 12 business days</strong> after artwork approval. Complex orders involving premium finishes (embossing, foil stamping, spot UV) may require additional time. Rush production may be available upon request — please <a href="/contact">contact us</a> to discuss availability and any associated fees.</p>

      <h2>2. Shipping Methods and Carriers</h2>
      <p>We ship all orders within the contiguous United States using trusted carriers including UPS, FedEx, and USPS. The specific carrier used for your order will depend on package weight, dimensions, destination, and availability at time of shipping.</p>
      <p>For large or pallet-sized orders, freight shipping may be arranged. Our team will communicate all shipping details prior to dispatch.</p>

      <h2>3. Estimated Delivery Timeframes</h2>
      <p>After your order ships, estimated transit times are:</p>
      <table class="spec-table">
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Delivery Zone</th><th>Estimated Transit Time</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Midwest (IL, IN, OH, MI, WI, MN)</td><td>1 – 2 Business Days</td></tr>
          <tr><td>East Coast (NY, PA, VA, FL, etc.)</td><td>2 – 4 Business Days</td></tr>
          <tr><td>South & Central USA</td><td>2 – 3 Business Days</td></tr>
          <tr><td>West Coast (CA, OR, WA, etc.)</td><td>3 – 5 Business Days</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Mountain / Southwest</td><td>2 – 4 Business Days</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Alaska & Hawaii</td><td>5 – 10 Business Days</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p>These are estimates only. Actual delivery times may vary based on carrier conditions, weather, or peak seasons. Transit time begins from the date of shipment, not the date of order.</p>

      <h2>4. Shipping Costs</h2>
      <p>Shipping costs are calculated based on package weight, dimensions, and destination, and will be included in your order quote. Any changes to the order after quotation that affect shipping costs will be communicated before finalization.</p>

      <h2>5. Order Tracking</h2>
      <p>Once your order has shipped, you will receive a tracking number via the email address provided during your order. You can use this tracking number on the carrier's website to monitor your shipment's progress.</p>

      <h2>6. Shipping Address Accuracy</h2>
      <p>Please ensure that your shipping address is accurate and complete at the time of ordering. The Candle Sleeves is not responsible for delays or failed deliveries caused by incorrect or incomplete shipping information. Address changes after shipment may incur additional fees charged by the carrier.</p>

      <h2>7. Damage During Shipping</h2>
      <p>We pack all orders carefully to minimize the risk of transit damage. If your order arrives visibly damaged, please:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Photograph the damaged packaging and products immediately upon receipt</li>
        <li>Note the damage on the carrier's delivery receipt if possible</li>
        <li>Contact us at Info@thecandlesleeves.com within 48 hours of delivery with photos and order details</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We will work with the carrier to file a damage claim and determine the appropriate resolution, which may include a replacement order.</p>

      <h2>8. Lost or Stolen Packages</h2>
      <p>If your tracking information shows "delivered" but you have not received your package, please check with neighbors or building management first. If the package cannot be located, contact us and we will assist in opening an investigation with the carrier.</p>

      <h2>9. International Shipping</h2>
      <p>Currently, we primarily serve US-based customers. For international shipping inquiries, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a> to discuss availability, lead times, and any applicable customs or duties.</p>

      <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>For shipping-related questions, please contact our team:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:Info@thecandlesleeves.com">Info@thecandlesleeves.com</a></li>
        <li><strong>Phone:</strong> (503) 358-0443</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
